<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>All Flags Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 50px;
            background-color: rgb(32, 32, 32);
            animation: fadeIn 4s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            0% {
                opacity: 0;
            }
            100% {
                opacity: 1;
            }
        }

        h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        p {
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .image-wrapper {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .image-wrapper img {
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #3b3b3b;
            color: #000000;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .text {
            color: rgb(32, 32, 32);
        }

        canvas {
            position: fixed;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 9999;
        }
    </style>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.3.1"></script>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            setInterval(function() {
                createConfetti();
            }, 1500);
        });

        function createConfetti() {
            var canvas = document.createElement('canvas');
            canvas.width = window.innerWidth;
            canvas.height = window.innerHeight;
            document.body.appendChild(canvas);

            confetti({
                particleCount: 100,
                spread: 160,
                origin: { y: 0.6 }
            });

            setTimeout(function() {
                document.body.removeChild(canvas);
            }, 3000);
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Félicitations !</h1>
    <p>Vous avez trouvé tous les flags et avez retrouvé votre ami Axel.</p>
    <p>Grâce à vous, les dangereux hackers Louis et Weuve le maléfique ne pourront plus commettre de méfaits.</p>
    <div class="image-wrapper">
        <img src="static/img/ezgif.com-gif-maker.gif" alt="Congratulations Image">
    </div>
    <a href="/" class="button">Retour à l'accueil</a>
    <div class="text">À suivre...</div>
</body>
</html>